  <brief_title>The Effect of EGD Probe Insertion on the Intracuff Pressure of the Laryngeal Mask Airway or Cuffed Endotracheal Tube in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of EGD Probe Insertion on the Intracuff Pressure of the Laryngeal Mask Airway or Cuffed Endotracheal Tube in Children</official_title>
