  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A prospective study designed to access changes in the intracuff pressure of a laryngeal mask
      airway (LMA) or cuffed endotracheal tube (cETT) during placement of an
      esophagogastroduodenoscopy (EGD) probe during an EGD in the pediatric population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
